<div class="container py-5">
  <div class="card shadow-sm">
    <div class="card-body">
      <h1 class="card-title text-center mb-4">Asteroid Game Help Center</h1>

      <hr>

      <h2 class="h4 mt-4">Controls</h2>
      <ul class="list-group list-group-flush mb-4">
        <li class="list-group-item"><strong>←</strong> Move left</li>
        <li class="list-group-item"><strong>→</strong> Move right</li>
        <li class="list-group-item"><strong>↑</strong> Move up</li>
        <li class="list-group-item"><strong>↓</strong> Move down</li>
        <li class="list-group-item"><strong>ENTER</strong> Start the game</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="h4">Game Modes</h2>
      <ul class="list-group list-group-flush mb-4">
        <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Easy</strong> – Slower asteroids and fewer of them at the start</li>
        <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Hard</strong> – Faster asteroids and more of them at the start</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="h4">Grading</h2>
      <p>If grading is enabled, your score will be submitted to your course when the game ends.</p>
      <p>The score is based on how many seconds you survive.</p>
      <ul class="list-group list-group-flush mb-4">
        <li class="list-group-item">
          <strong>Easy Mode:</strong><br>
          Survive <strong>50 seconds or more</strong> → <strong>Full credit (1.0)</strong><br>
          Less than 50 seconds → partial score
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item">
          <strong>Hard Mode:</strong><br>
          Survive <strong>20 seconds or more</strong> → <strong>Full credit (1.0)</strong><br>
          Less than 20 seconds → partial score
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
